<I><FONT COLOR="#B22222">-- $Id: regexmatch-lua.code,v 1.2 2004-11-08 08:15:19 bfulgham Exp $
</FONT></I><I><FONT COLOR="#B22222">-- http://shootout.alioth.debian.org
